{"tid":1027683,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"獵頭公司出價係咪永遠9吹","createTime":"2019-02-19T03:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T11:13:53.000Z","uid":180913,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b89f24a2b55e8e129ff9e85faf8b81ba1f03157e","tid":1027683,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"見過幾份<br />\n（  第一份） 一去到未in就話in個份無哂位叫你去in另一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（咁你叫我黎jm9)<br />\n查完差價起碼食5千<br />\n<br />\n（ 第二份）<br />\n係咁chur你去見 講到幾高人工 話有14000一個月（網頁話連勤工去到14000未計ot）<br />\n去到in同你講得9千幾仲要10個鐘 加ot先去到14000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 47蚊ot要幾耐先去到14000？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要 個獵頭公司 之後打過嚟問我見成點<br />\n，我講話in左5分鐘<br />\n佢係度話我有冇搞錯 in咁少時間<br />\n之後直接cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（ 第三份）<br />\n網頁打明見過幾份<br />\n（  第一份） 一去到未in就話in個份無哂位叫你去in另一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（咁你叫我黎jm9)<br />\n查完差價起碼食5千<br />\n<br />\n（ 第二份）<br />\n係咁chur你去見 講到幾高人工 話有14000一個月（網頁話連勤工去到14000未計ot）<br />\n去到in同你講得9千幾仲要10個鐘 加ot先去到14000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 47蚊ot要幾耐先去到14000？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要 個獵頭公司 之後打過嚟問我見成點<br />\n，我講話in<br />\n<br />\n見過幾份<br />\n（  第一份） 一去到未in就話in個份無哂位叫你去in另一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（咁你叫我黎jm9)<br />\n查完差價起碼食5千。<br />\n<br />\n（ 第二份）<br />\n係咁chur你去見 講到幾高人工 話有14000一個月（網頁話連勤工去到14000未計ot）<br />\n去到in同你講得9千幾仲要10個鐘 加ot先去到14000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 47蚊ot要幾耐先去到 14000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後個hr係我in完打番電話黎，<br />\n問我in成點，我話in左十分鐘都無<br />\n之後佢本身一直都好好禮貌之後突然：吓 十分鐘都無 咁無啦<br />\n之後直接88都無就cut線<br />\n<br />\n（第三份）<br />\n個page度打明15000+2000（  夜間津貼），標題打16000－17000<br />\nps佢要求既條件我都符合<br />\n一打到phone in 5成時間話學歷  其他見工嘅人要做比較 點點點點（講到你點差，話10000都好啦.）<br />\n之後我同佢話我而加都唔只，佢話咁11000都好啦（自己係度自high咁）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬 你一係打明起薪係10000<br />\n我照send cv係我既事，等人地唔好哂時間同埋預期錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n一陣去見工<br />\n17000蚊個post頂薪係咪用黎呃人去in?<br />\n有冇方法點樣還價？<br />\n定其實一早已經fixed死哂？<br />\n<br />\n有冇做hr可以教下路點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27293c25cd2a104502b2b794d88bbfdfae306cf1","tid":1027683,"uid":127511,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"你學歷都幾低下。"},{"pid":"cfb95fb878bd74179b7d68338a8fbec53ec1f3a7","tid":1027683,"uid":37448,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"睇你repeat 咗幾次唔知點解覺得好好笑<br />\n不過你見得好自己好少壓你價, 大不了咪唔撚做<br />\n記得而家係工搵人, 好多行都唔夠人做野呀"},{"pid":"b4c59ee1507ec043b2a9c649e710928475dde60a","tid":1027683,"uid":37448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你repeat 咗幾次唔知點解覺得好好笑<br />\n不過你見得好<del>自己</del>好少壓你價, 大不了咪唔撚做<br />\n記得而家係工搵人, 好多行都唔夠人做野呀</blo